  "description": "All odd dividers: \u00f73, \u00f75, \u00f77 \u2014 Oskar Sala's alien complete set. bodyFreq=28Hz: seismic, below pitch, felt in the chest. 4-second attack, 6-second release. This preset does not respond to human time. A note played here takes geological patience to arrive and an epoch to fade. The odd harmonics wobble like tectonic plates. The body at 28Hz is not a musical event \u2014 it is a condition of the habitat.",
